"      </a>",
"      above)",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      Reduction in recurrent myocardial infarction and ischemia (see",
"      <a class=\"local\" href=\"#H6\">",
"       'Reduction in recurrent myocardial infarction and ischemia'",
"      </a>",
"      above)",
"     </li>",
"     <li>",
"      Reduction in sudden death (see",
"      <a class=\"local\" href=\"#H7\">",
"       'Reduction in sudden death'",
"      </a>",
"      above)",
"     </li>",
"    </ul>",
"   </p>",
